Nautilus-Image-Converter
========================

The Nautilus-Image-Converter extension allows you to resize/rotate images from Nautilus.

Hacking:
========

n-i-c can be check out with the following command:

git clone https://gitlab.gnome.org/coreyberla/nautilus-image-converter.git

Patches welcomed!

Installing:
========
sudo apt install libgtk-4-dev libnautilus-extension4 libnautilus-extension-dev gettext
meson build
ninja -C build
sudo ninja install -C build
